<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>《＠守望》第51期——社会服务 on 北京守望教会</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/categories/%E5%AE%88%E6%9C%9B%E7%AC%AC51%E6%9C%9F%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1/</link><description>Recent content in 《＠守望》第51期——社会服务 on 北京守望教会</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2013 09:22:10 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://shwchurch3.github.io/categories/%E5%AE%88%E6%9C%9B%E7%AC%AC51%E6%9C%9F%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>《＠守望》第51期——社会服务</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2013/07/03/%E7%AE%80%E8%AE%AF-40/</link><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2013 09:22:10 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2013/07/03/%E7%AE%80%E8%AE%AF-40/</guid><description>简讯： 1、 6月16日，本主日共有30位弟兄姊妹因参加户外敬拜被扣留，1位姊妹礼拜五晚被住宾馆。至当日上午10：55左右，所有被扣留的弟兄姊妹</description></item><item><title>基督徒的社会责任/孙毅长老</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2013/07/03/%E5%9F%BA%E7%9D%A3%E5%BE%92%E7%9A%84%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E8%B4%A3%E4%BB%BB%E5%AD%99%E6%AF%85%E9%95%BF%E8%80%81/</link><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2013 09:21:34 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2013/07/03/%E5%9F%BA%E7%9D%A3%E5%BE%92%E7%9A%84%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E8%B4%A3%E4%BB%BB%E5%AD%99%E6%AF%85%E9%95%BF%E8%80%81/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;当我们说基督徒应有其社会关怀或责任时，我们并不是要承担在这个地上建立什么样的天国的责任。这些都是过于刻板和狭窄的理解。圣经只教导我们爱身边那一个个活生生的人，而不是某种抽象的群体或非人格化的制度。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>同性恋带给福音怎样的挑战？ ——从美国最高法院否决《捍卫婚姻法案》引发开来</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2013/07/03/%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%81%8B%E5%B8%A6%E7%BB%99%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B3%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E7%9A%84%E6%8C%91%E6%88%98-%E4%BB%8E%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2/</link><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2013 09:20:47 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2013/07/03/%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%81%8B%E5%B8%A6%E7%BB%99%E